library(ggplot2)
ggplot(data) + 
  geom_histogram(aes(x=,y=..density..), position="identity") +

library(GGally)
set.seed(10000)
data.samp <- subset(data, select = c(4:8))
data.samp <- data.samp[sample(1:length(data$), 5000), ]
ggpairs(data.samp,
        lower = list(continuous = wrap("points", shape = I('.'))),
        upper = list(combo = wrap("box", outlier.shape = I('.')))) +
  theme(text=element_text(family="Heiti TC Light"))

require(coefplot)
## Loading required package: coefplot
m2 <- lm( ~  +  - 1,  data = data)
coefplot(m2, xlab = '', ylab = '', title = ' = ') +
  theme(text=element_text(family="Heiti TC Light"))

fit_m2 <- data.frame(data[, c(1, 6, 2)], fitted = fitted(m2), resid = resid(m2),
                     infl = influence(m2)$hat )

ggplot(data = fit_m2, aes(x = , group = )) +
  stat_density(geom = 'path', position = 'identity') +
  stat_density(geom = 'path', position = 'identity', aes(x = fitted)) +
  geom_vline(xintercept = c(with(data, tapply(,, mean))), linetype = 'dotted')+
  facet_grid( ~ .) +
  scale_x_continuous(breaks = seq(200, 900, by = 100))+
  labs(x = '', y = '') +
  theme(text=element_text(family="Heiti TC Light"))
